''' Write a code that uses a lambda function to find the maximum of three given numbers '''

#lambda function to find maximum of three numbers
maximum=lambda x,y,z: x if (x>y and x>z) else (y if y>z else z)

#example
num1=453
num2=435
num3=819

result=maximum(num1,num2,num3)
print("Maximum is ",result)
